{
    combination : [ 'move', 'move' ],
    strategy : [
        { play : score = play.wordScore }
    ]
},
{
    combination : [ 'attack', 'move' ],
    strategy : [
        { attack : () => { score = 0 }},
        { move : () => { score = move.score - (attack.wordScore * attack.attackMultiplier) }}
    ]
},
{
    combination : [ 'attack', 'attack' ],
    strategy : [
        { play :   () => { score = play.score * play.attackMultiplier }},
        { winner : () => { score = 0 }},
        { loser :  () => { score = -1 * attack.wordScore * attack.attackMultiplier }}
    ]
},

   
When you can Attack
turns increment AttackMultiplier
high scoring words increment AttackMultiplier
make AttackMultipliers collectable
